                    <h1 class="resources-hero-title" style="color: white;" data-reveal>Learning Modules</h1>
                    <p class="resources-hero-subtitle" style="margin-left: 0;" data-reveal>
                        Our learning modules are designed to help you go beyond the textbook and explore the rich, often-overlooked layers of the natural world. Each module is an invitation to discover, develop, and nurture a deep sense of wonder through hands-on activities and engaging resources.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        {{!-- 2. Resource Grid --}}
        <section class="site-section">
            <div class="container">
                {{!-- 3. Resource Grid --}}
                <div class="resource-item-grid">
                    {{!-- Water Module --}}
